6
00:00:20,520 --> 00:00:23,090
We have explored in detail the second phase

7
00:00:23,090 --> 00:00:27,800
of the project life cycle, which we refer to as planning.

8
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:31,030
We emphasised the importance of the planning phase of the life

9
00:00:31,030 --> 00:00:35,110
cycle, as it is the most important phase since failing

10
00:00:35,110 --> 00:00:39,000
to plan usually means planning to fail.

11
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,440
Planning properly and in sufficient detail

12
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:44,660
is essential to project success.

13
00:00:44,660 --> 00:00:47,080
We highlighted that the three key areas that

14
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:50,720
need to be planned in detail are the scope, scheduling,

15
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:53,330
and costing of the project.

16
00:00:53,330 --> 00:00:55,280
It is encouraged that action planning

17
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:58,190
is used to help you determine the activities that

18
00:00:58,190 --> 00:01:01,300
need to be completed by whom and by when

19
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:04,900
so that the main objectives of the project are met.

20
